<section class="section section--pbs-0">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div class="page-head">
          <div class="breadcrumbs">
            <div class="breadcrumbs-content">
              <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}" class="breadcrumbs-item">
                <span class="breadcrumbs-item-text">Home</span>
              </a>
              <a href="{{ pages['spotlight'].url }}" class="breadcrumbs-item">
                <span class="breadcrumbs-item-text">{{ pages.spotlight.title }}</span>
              </a>
              <a href="{{ request.path }}" class="breadcrumbs-item breadcrumbs-item--active">
                <span class="breadcrumbs-item-text">{{ page.title }}</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="page-head-info">
            <h2 class="page-title">INGRAINED: Wood in a Cross-Section of Time, Koel Gallery</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="spotlight-hero">
          <div class="spotlight-hero-media">
            <img
              class="spotlight-hero-media-img"
              src="{{ 'spotlights-hero-2.jpg' | asset_url }}"
              alt="Spotlight"
              height=""
              width=""
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="subsection-section">
          <div class="subsection-section-content">
            <div class="subsection-section-head">
              <h3 class="subsection-section-title">Exhibition — Koel Gallery Karachi</h3>
              <div class="subsection-section-description">
                <p>
                  Wood has been my muse for two decades. This exhibition is a love letter to the trees that have carried
                  our stories far longer than we have walked among them.
                </p>
                <p>
                  At the generous invitation of Noor Jehan Bilgrami at Koel Gallery, curating this show alongside my
                  dear friend Naila Mahmood was a treasured experience. It taught me, moved me, and changed how I think
                  about my own practice. Ingrained is a celebration of wood and a tribute to the incredible
                  participating artists whose imagination and hands have brought it alive.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection-section-body">
              <div class="individual-spotlight-gallery">
                <div class="individual-spotlight-gallery-item">
                  <img
                    class="individual-spotlight-gallery-img"
                    src="{{ 'individual-spotlight-1.jpg' | asset_url }}"
                    alt="Spotlight 1"
                    height=""
                    width=""
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="individual-spotlight-gallery-item">
                  <img
                    class="individual-spotlight-gallery-img"
                    src="{{ 'individual-spotlight-2.jpg' | asset_url }}"
                    alt="Spotlight 1"
                    height=""
                    width=""
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="individual-spotlight-gallery-item">
                  <img
                    class="individual-spotlight-gallery-img"
                    src="{{ 'individual-spotlight-3.jpg' | asset_url }}"
                    alt="Spotlight 1"
                    height=""
                    width=""
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="subsection-section">
          <div class="subsection-section-content">
            <div
              class="subsection-section-head subsection-section-head--center"
            >
              <h3 class="subsection-section-title">Curatorial Statement - An Invitation To Listen To The Wood</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection-section-body">
              <div class="individual-spotlight-highlights">
                <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight">
                  <h3 class="individual-spotlight-highlight-title">Living Witness</h3>
                  <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight-text">
                    <p>
                      As living witnesses, trees mirror our personal and collective histories. The exhibition celebrates
                      how they hold the weight of national identities, cultural memory, and the struggle over land and
                      ecology. As we read wood, we in essence enter a dialogue with time — layered, resilient, and
                      profoundly alive.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight">
                  <h3 class="individual-spotlight-highlight-title">Tethered To Trees</h3>
                  <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight-text">
                    <p>
                      The exhibition explores the intricate bond between humans and trees — a bond we have too often
                      betrayed, felling forests without reverence and denying the sanctity with which they hold our
                      ecosystems, our histories, and our very existence in balance.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight">
                  <h3 class="individual-spotlight-highlight-title">Rooted In Time</h3>
                  <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight-text">
                    <p>
                      In the architecture of wood, time quietly reveals itself. Trees carry the memory of growth,
                      rupture, and renewal within their bodies. The exhibition explores how trees are more than
                      material; they are metaphors of rootedness and resilience, of belonging and displacement, of
                      innovation and legacy.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight">
                  <h3 class="individual-spotlight-highlight-title">The Subject & The Medium</h3>
                  <div class="individual-spotlight-highlight-text">
                    <p>
                      A vessel of texture, grain, and warmth, inviting touch and transformation in the artisans hands.
                      As they carve, join, turn and finish, they read the wood's memory, responding with awareness and
                      understanding.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
